Bit Extraction:
  L1 Index (bits 31-22) = 1
  L2 Index (bits 21-12) = 3
  Offset   (bits 11-0)  = 4 (0x004)

L1 Table Lookup:
  L1[1] = 5000 (base address of L2 table)

L2 Table Lookup:
  L2[3] = 7 (frame number)

Physical Address Calculation:
  Physical = Frame × Page Size + Offset
  Physical = 7 × 4096 + 4
  Physical = 28672 + 4
  Physical = 28676 (0x07004)

Summary:
